Vladimir Nabokov





TO: MAURICE GIRODIAS

CC, 1 p.

Ithaca, N.Y.





March 10, 1957

Dear Mr. Girodias,

I have carefully read your letter of March 5, wherein you urge me to reconsider my decision in regard to lolitigation.

